divs: Sighting DetailsAt the given and indicated date and time, I noticed the objects appearing on the north western sky, traveling at a slower speed towards a south eastern direction. At an angle of about 15 degrees to the east from my position, the individual lights diminished to the point of invisibility.
Summary: traveling at between 2-3000 feet altitude in almost straight line.
